title: XML to SQL Conversion v6
author: Mohammed Ali Shaik
description:
This asset takes XML file used for informatica pipelines and converts it into SQL query.  
Requirements needed to run the code is the environment variables. 
command to execute this command is streamlit run app.py PROJECT_ID IBM_CLOUD_URL API_KEY IAM_URL SPACE_ID ENDPOINT_URL1 ENDPOINT_URL2
In the above command ENDPOINT_URL1 and ENDPOINT_URL2 are the deployed prompt template end point urls.
